-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/germany-confident-eu-to-ban-state-debt-cds-speculation-ftd-says.html
Germany ’s government is confident
that the European Union will outlaw speculation with credit-
default swaps on sovereign debt,  Financial Times Deutschland 
reported, citing an unnamed German EU emissary.  The region’s member states and the European parliament will
today discuss rules on short-selling, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
